stream
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 720.0 Td (pre-approval may be granted by the VP Supply Chain, but written confirmation must) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 704.0 Td (follow within 24 hours.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 680.0 Td (4. NON-PREFERRED VENDOR USE IN EMERGENCIES) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 664.0 Td (When no preferred vendor can fulfil an emergency requirement within the required) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 648.0 Td (lead time, a non-preferred vendor may be used provided:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 632.0 Td (\(a\) The requisition is classified as critical urgency; and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 616.0 Td (\(b\) Manager approval is obtained regardless of the order amount; and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 600.0 Td (\(c\) A post-event vendor qualification review is initiated within 30 days.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 576.0 Td (5. DOCUMENTATION REQUIREMENTS) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 560.0 Td (All emergency procurement events must be documented within 5 business days in the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 544.0 Td (Emergency Procurement Register maintained by the procurement team. Documentation) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 528.0 Td (must include: the trigger event, the quantity and material procured, the vendor) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 512.0 Td (selected, the approval chain, and the total value of the emergency purchase) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 496.0 Td (order.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 72.0 472.0 Td (6. AUDIT AND REVIEW) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 456.0 Td (The VP Supply Chain reviews all emergency procurement events quarterly. Patterns) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 440.0 Td (of repeated emergency procurement for the same material indicate a forecasting or) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 424.0 Td (safety-stock calibration failure and must be escalated to the demand planning) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72.0 408.0 Td (team.) Tj ET
endstream
